data.name: TableAutoFormatField
desc: represents a field in an AutoFormat.
A field contains all cell properties for a specific position in an AutoFormat.
**since**

properties.name: CellBackColor
desc: contains the cell background color.

properties.name: CharColor
desc: contains the value of the text color.

properties.name: CharContoured
desc: is TRUE if the characters are contoured.

properties.name: CharCrossedOut
desc: is TRUE if the characters are crossed out.

properties.name: CharFontCharSet
desc: contains the value of the character set of the western font.

properties.name: CharFontCharSetAsian
desc: contains the value of the character set of the Asian font.

properties.name: CharFontCharSetComplex
desc: contains the value of the character set of the complex font.

properties.name: CharFontFamily
desc: contains the value of the western font family.

properties.name: CharFontFamilyAsian
desc: contains the value of the Asian font family.

properties.name: CharFontFamilyComplex
desc: contains the value of the complex font family.

properties.name: CharFontName
desc: specifies the name of the western font.

properties.name: CharFontNameAsian
desc: specifies the name of the Asian font.

properties.name: CharFontNameComplex
desc: specifies the name of the complex font.

properties.name: CharFontPitch
desc: contains the value of the pitch of the western font.

properties.name: CharFontPitchAsian
desc: contains the value of the pitch of the Asian font.

properties.name: CharFontPitchComplex
desc: contains the value of the pitch of the complex font.

properties.name: CharFontStyleName
desc: specifies the name of the western font style.

properties.name: CharFontStyleNameAsian
desc: specifies the name of the Asian font style.

properties.name: CharFontStyleNameComplex
desc: specifies the name of the complex font style.

properties.name: CharHeight
desc: contains the height of characters of the western font in point.

properties.name: CharHeightAsian
desc: contains the height of characters of the Asian font in point.

properties.name: CharHeightComplex
desc: contains the height of characters of the complex font in point.

properties.name: CharPosture
desc: contains the value of the posture of characters of the western font.

properties.name: CharPostureAsian
desc: contains the value of the posture of characters of the Asian font.

properties.name: CharPostureComplex
desc: contains the value of the posture of characters of the complex font.

properties.name: CharShadowed
desc: is TRUE if the characters are shadowed.

properties.name: CharUnderline
desc: contains the value for the character underline.

properties.name: CharWeight
desc: contains the value for the weight of characters of the western font.

properties.name: CharWeightAsian
desc: contains the value for the weight of characters of the Asian font.

properties.name: CharWeightComplex
desc: contains the value for the weight of characters of the complex font.

properties.name: HoriJustify
desc: specifies the horizontal alignment of the cell contents.

properties.name: IsCellBackgroundTransparent
desc: is TRUE if the cell background is transparent.
In this case the TableAutoFormatField.CellBackColor value is not used.

properties.name: IsTextWrapped
desc: is TRUE if text breaks automatically at cell borders.

properties.name: Orientation
desc: contains the orientation of the cell contents (i.e.
top-to-bottom or stacked).

properties.name: ParaBottomMargin
desc: contains the margin between cell contents and bottom border (in 1/100 mm).

properties.name: ParaLeftMargin
desc: contains the margin between cell contents and left border (in 1/100 mm).

properties.name: ParaRightMargin
desc: contains the margin between cell contents and right border (in 1/100 mm).

properties.name: ParaTopMargin
desc: contains the margin between cell contents and top border (in 1/100 mm).

properties.name: RotateAngle
desc: contains the rotation angle of the cell contents.

properties.name: RotateReference
desc: contains the reference edge of the cell rotation.
changed from com.sun.star.table.CellVertJustify to long in LibO 3.5

properties.name: ShadowFormat
desc: contains a description of the shadow.

properties.name: TableBorder
desc: property containing a description of the cell border.
**since**

properties.name: TableBorder2
desc: property containing a description of the cell border.
Preferred over com.sun.star.table.TableBorder TableBorder.
**since**
LibreOffice 3.6

properties.name: VertJustify
desc: specifies the vertical alignment of the cell contents.
changed from com.sun.star.table.CellVertJustify to long in LibO 3.5
